name: Mackenzie Ivy Global Equity ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks long term capital growth. The Fund consistent with protection of capital, by investing primarily in a broad range of equities within developed markets anywhere in the world. The ETF's investments may include investments in emerging markets, and securities of US companies will usually form the largest percentage of assets from any geographic area.
